25 October 2010Minister for Performance Monitoring and Evaluation, Collins Chabane, Minister of Rural Development and Land Reform, Gugile Nkwinti and Minister of Economic Development, Ebrahim Patel will brief the media on the outcome of the Special Cabinet meeting which was held today Monday, 25th October 2010.Details are as follows:Date: Tuesday, 26 October 2010 Time: 11h00 Venue: Union Buildings, Room 153There will be a live video link-up to Imbizo Media Centre in Cape Town.For media inquiries contact:Neo Momodu Cell: 079 462-5081Media are requested to RSVP with:David Masango Cell: 083 279 7520Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)